These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different games are played: billiard, canasta, whist, domino
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, bluemaster, pall-mall, chaman
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, project-manager, videographer, manager
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, gospel, d&b, r&b
 1. the project-manager is not to the right of the entrepreneur##8
 2. the fan of dubstep is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
 3. the fan of r&b is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the entrepreneur is not to the left of the manager##8
 5. the fan of dubstep is not to the right of the fan of dubstep##8
 6. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the manager##1
 7. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
 8. the chaman-smoker is between the fan of gospel and the project-manager##2
 9. the fan of r&b is the pall-mall-smoker##1
10. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person playing domino##1
11. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3
12. the person playing domino is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5
13. the pall-mall-smoker is not to the left of the fan of r&b##8
14. the person playing canasta is the fan of d&b##1
15. the person playing canasta is not the project-manager##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Game         | billiard     | canasta   | domino | whist |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | chaman   | dunhill   | pall-mall  |
| Job         | project-manager  | videographer  | manager  | entrepreneur |
| Music-Genre     | dubstep    | d&b | gospel     | r&b    |

