The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, april, february, july
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, dannemann, davidoff, blend
 1. the person who's birthday is in february is between the dunhill-smoker and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 2. the person who's sport is volleyball is not to the right of the dannemann-smoker##8
 3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
 4. the person who's sport is parkour-polo is not to the right of the blend-smoker##8
 5. the dunhill-smoker is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8
 6. the modern house is not to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##8
 7. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere to the left of the blend-smoker##5
 8. the davidoff-smoker is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is the dannemann-smoker##1
10. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3
11. the dunhill-smoker is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##8
12. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
13. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the art-deco house##5
14. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
15. the person who's sport is parkour-polo is on the far left or far right##3
16. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
17. the person who's sport is parkour-polo is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##8
18. the art-deco house is not to the right of the dannemann-smoker##8
19. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the art-deco house##1

