.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, blood-red, ivory, lavender
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, soy-milk, lemonade
There 4 different types of food: cherry, spinach, cabbage, garlic
City: london, paris, hamburg, venice
 1. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 2. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ivory##5
 3. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
 4. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the right of the person eating cherry##5
 5. the person traveling to hamburg is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
 6. the person who likes lavender is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
 7. the person eating cabbage is in an odd position##4
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
10. the person traveling to paris is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking coffee is not to the left of the person eating spinach##8
12. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Color         | orange    | lavender   | ivory | blood-red |
| Beverage   | coffee     | soy-milk  | lemonade   | iced-tea      |
| Food   | spinach | cherry    | cabbage      | garlic       |
| City         | hamburg    | london | venice   | paris    |

