The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, car, roller, train
 1. the person playing backgammon is not to the left of the owner of the snake##8
 2. the teacher is the owner of the ferret##1
 3. the person driving the car is not the owner of the snake##6
 4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 5. the person playing backgammon is not to the right of the electrician##8
 6. the person driving the roller is not to the right of the person playing backgammon##8
 7. the person driving the car is not to the left of the owner of the ferret##8
 8. the lawyer is the person playing canasta##1
 9. the freelancer is not to the left of the owner of the turtle##8
10. the person playing poker is not to the left of the person playing backgammon##8
11. the person driving the train is between the owner of the turtle and the person playing canasta##2
12. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
13. the lawyer is not to the right of the person playing canasta##8
14. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
