 6. the person driving the bike is the person driving the bike##1
 7. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
 8. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
 9. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
10. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
11. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3
12. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
13. the person who's sport is handball is not to the left of the person driving the ship##8
14. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the person driving the bike##8
15. the person driving the airplane is the person drinking fanta##1
16. the person driving the tram is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Transport           | tram | airplane       | ship      | bike  |
| Beverage   | sprite    | fanta | almond-milk   | water   |
| Pet   | turtle   | goldfish          | hedgehog      | rat  |
| Sport   | climbing   | skiing      | surfing | handball |

